al-Yadam. Place the onion
in a saucepan. Add 2 cups
of water. Cook until all
the water is absorbed and
the onions are browned.
8.While stirring, add 1 cup
water, raisins, fat, the alYadam spice mixture, and
salt. Fry for a few
minutes.
9.Place the food on a plate.
Spread the al-Yadam on
top.
